# This directory contains critical scripts for the Wikibooks recipe automation workflow
# DO NOT DELETE these mandatory files:
#
# WORKFLOW STEPS:
# ===============
#
# STEP 1: Extract Recipes from Wikibooks
#   - extract-wikibooks-recipe.js (Extracts recipes and images from Wikibooks)
#   - wikibooks-urls.txt (Input file with Wikibooks recipe URLs)
#   - Triggered by: npm run wiki:extract
#   - Output: scripts/wiki/output/*-wikibooks-raw.json + images
#
# STEP 2: Convert to MongoDB Format
#   - convert-and-upload.js (Main orchestrator)
#   - convert-wikibooks-with-assistant.js (ChatGPT conversion using Assistant API)
#   - CHAT_GPT_PROMPT_TEMPLATE.md (ChatGPT system prompt for conversion)
#   - Triggered by: npm run convert-and-upload
#   - Output: scripts/wiki/output/chatGPT/{slug}.json
#
# STEP 3: Upload to MongoDB
#   - upload-gpt-to-mongodb.js (Uploads converted recipes to MongoDB)
#   - Triggered by: npm run upload-gpt-to-mongodb
#   - Output: Recipes in MongoDB receptai.recipes_new collection
#   - Moves ChatGPT JSON to: scripts/wiki/output/chatGPT/uploaded-to-mongodb/
#   - Moves original wiki JSON to: scripts/wiki/output/processed/wiki-raw-recipes/
#
# STEP 4: Process Images and Upload to S3
#   - See: scripts/.gitkeep-wiki-automation (image-prep-and-load.js)
#   - Triggered by: npm run image-prep-and-load
#   - Output: Images in S3 + MongoDB updated with S3 URLs
#
# DOCUMENTATION:
#   - output/workFlow.md (Complete workflow documentation)
#
# These files are protected by .gitkeep to prevent accidental deletion

